to run the different fortran codes:
	copy the local folder to ela (using windows with PuTTY secure copy, maybe delete large data files for faster upload):
		pscp -r 'D:\Dropbox\(2021-2023) ETH\...\vNN_group6_openACC' class193@ela.cscs.ch:/users/class193/
	login to daint:
		ssh class193@ela.cscs.ch
		ssh daint.cscs.ch
		cd vNN_group6_openACC
	run:
		bash run.sh
			(enter version)
			(enter nx=ny)
	plot:
		bash plot.sh
	logout:
		exit
		exit

to download the folder to the local machine:
	pscp -r class193@ela.cscs.ch:/users/class193/vNN_group6_openACC/ 'D:\Dropbox\(2021-2023) ETH\...\vNN_group6_openACC'

to download specific files to the local machine:
	pscp -r class193@ela.cscs.ch:/users/class193/vNN_group6_openACC/data/*acc0[1-3, 5]* 'D:\Dropbox\(2021-2023) ETH\...\vNN_group6_openACC\data'



